@startuml
title Диаграмма состояний\n"Жизненный цикл запроса на прогноз"

[*] --> New

New --> Validating : submit()
Validating --> Preprocessing : data_ok
Validating --> Error : data_invalid

Preprocessing --> Predicting : features_ready
Preprocessing --> Error : preprocess_failed

Predicting --> Completed : prediction_ready
Predicting --> Error : model_failed

Completed --> Archived : save_history()

Error --> New : correct_and_resubmit()
Archived --> [*]

@enduml